<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">يريد:</span>» الظِّلال <span class="c2">«و»</span> عَرِدّا «: بَارِداً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>